# raw-sources/.ingest-allowlist
#
# Newline-separated path globs the wiki agent MAY read from raw-sources/.
# Anything not matched is off-limits unless explicitly added.
# Comments start with #. Globs are relative to raw-sources/.
#
# Conservative default: instrument-related vault folders, clippings,
# recent daily notes, making, outdoors, wrfcoin. Sensitive folders
# (Healthcare, Finance, IP, LLM Conversations, Inboxes, Archive) stay off.

# Vault folders are numbered; entries below reflect actual folder names.
second-brain/01 - Instruments/**
second-brain/04 - Making and Fabrication/**
second-brain/05 - Outdoors/**
second-brain/06 - Wrfcoin/**
second-brain/Clippings/**

# qmd collection 'obsidian' indexes these via ~/qmd-staging/second-brain/
# symlinks. To add a folder to the index, symlink it under the staging dir
# and add the corresponding entry here.

obsidian-clips/**

inbox/**
processed/**

